inimizeDescriptionLine": 1, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1014348, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O Allah, to You am I turning my face and with You do I keep my family members, my property, and everything with which You have allowed me to behave. I have trusted in You; so, do not disappoint me. O He Who saves those who trust in Him from disappointment and He Who does not give up those whom He safeguards. O Allah, (please do) send blessings upon Muhammad and the Household of Muhammad and guard me under Your custody, since nothing that You guard may be ruined.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Ay Ma’bood! Mai ne apna rukh Teri taraf kiya aur mai ne apna maal apna kunbah aur jo kuchh Tu ne diya hai sab kuchh Tere supurd (hawaale) kiya aur Tujh par bharosa kiya hai, pas tahi-dast (kisi ka mohtaaj) na kar, ay woh jo tahi-dast (mohtaaj) nahi karta jo uski taraf aaye woh goom nahi hota jis ki woh hifaazat kare. Hazrat Muhammad (s.a.w.a) aur Aale Muhammad (a.s) rehmat farma aur mujh ko apni nighraani mein rakh kyu’n keh jo Teri hifaazat mein ho woh zaaye (barbaad) nahi hota.", "Urdu": "اے معبود!میں نے اپنا رخ تیری طرف کیا اور میں نے اپنا مال اپنا کنبہ اور جو کچھ تو نے دیا ہے سب کچھ تیرے سپرد کیا اور تجھ پر بھروسہ کیا ہے، پس تنگ دست نہ کر اے وہ جو تنگ دست نہیں کرتا جو اس کی طرف آئے وہ گم نہیں ہوتا جس کی وہ حفاظت کرے، حضرت محمدؐ اور آل محمدؐ پر رحمت فرما اور مجھ کو اپنی نگرانی میں رکھ کیوں کہ جو تیری حفاظت میں ہو وہ ضائع نہیں ہوتا۔", "RArabic": "ALLAAHUMMA ELAYKA WAJJAHTO WA A’LAYKA KHALLAFTO AHLEE WA MAALEE WA MAA KHAWWALTANEE WA BEKA WASIQTO FALAA TOKHAYYIBNEE YAA MAN LAA YOKHAYYEBO MAN ARAAADAHU WA LAA YOZAYYE-O’ MAN HAFEZAHU SALLE A’LAA MOHAMMADIN WA AALE MOHAMMADIN WAH-FAZNEE BE HIFZEKA FA-INNAHU LAA YOZEE-O’ MAN HAFIZTA.", "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰہُمَّ اِلَیْکَ وَجَّہْتُ وَجْہِیْ وَعَلَیْکَ خَلَّفْتُ اَہْلِیْ وَمَالِیْ وَمَا خَوَّلْتَنِیْ وَبِکَ وَثِقْتُ فَلَا تُخَیِّبْنِیْ یَا مَنْ لَّا یُخَیِّبُ مَنْ اَرَادَہٗ وَلَا یُضَیِّعُ مَنْ حَفِظَہٗ صَلِّ عَلٰی مُحَمَّدٍ وَّاٰلِ مُحَمَّدٍ وَاحْفَظْنِیْ بِحِفْظِکَ فَاِنَّہٗ لَا یَضِیْعُ مَنْ خَفِظْتَ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "Arabi